data.description:
RD LOAN ELIGIBLE!!! This serene home offers beauty in a natural setting. Featuring 2 bedrooms plus an office, a two-sided fireplace, and abundant natural light. The open living area connects to a well-appointed kitchen with ample storage and island granite. The master bedroom includes a walk-in closet, spacious tub, and separate shower. Storage options abound with a tall crawlspace and garage storage.
Ideal for Bella Vista amenities, it's only 2 miles to Loch Lomond Marina, 5 miles to recreation centers, and a short drive to various attractions. Access Walmart in 8 miles and Bentonville Square in 13 miles. The yard is low-maintenance with rockscaping and a 3/4 covered deck for outdoor relaxation.
